## 🔒 Security Features

| Feature | Implementation |
|---------|-----------------|
| **Authentication** | JWT with 24-hour expiration |
| **Password Hashing** | BCrypt (12+ salt rounds) |
| **Authorization** | Role-based (Admin, Developer, QA) |
| **Audit Logging** | All user actions tracked with IP & timestamp |
| **Input Validation** | FluentValidation on all endpoints |
| **SQL Injection** | Parameterized queries via Entity Framework |
| **CORS** | Configured for specific origins |
| **Error Handling** | Generic error messages (no info leakage) |

